data.description: Welcome to this well maintained duplex, presenting an exceptional investment opportunity. Boasting a total of four bedrooms split evenly between its two units, this property ensures comfortable living spaces for tenants or small families. With separate utilities for each unit, managing expenses becomes effortless for both landlords and tenants alike. Off-street parking further enhances convenience, offering hassle-free accessibility. Enjoying proximity to the picturesque Capron Park, residents can indulge in outdoor recreation and relaxation at their leisure. Both units are equipped with laundry hook-ups. Unit B features a finished basement, providing additional living space or storage potential. Overall, this duplex exemplifies quality and presents an enticing prospect for investors seeking a well-cared-for property in a prime location. Don't miss the chance to explore the possibilities this duplex offers.
